{"id":148263,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/4-27-左小祖咒在上海机场被警方扣押数小时后释放/","date":"2011-04-28T06:30:40Z","modified":"2011-09-27T16:54:38Z","title":"4.27 左小祖咒在上海机场被警方扣押数小时后释放","content":"<p><p align=\"left\"><b><span><span><br /></span></span></b></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><b><span><span>音乐人左小祖咒在上海机场被扣押数小时后释放（</span></span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2011.4.27</span></span></b><b><span><span>）</span></span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></b></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><b><span><span><br /></span></span></b></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2011</span></span><span><span>年</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>4</span></span><span><span>月</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>27</span></span><span><span>日下午约</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>4</span></span><span><span>点，中国知名音乐人左小祖咒及妻子、乐评人张晓舟在上海机场遭警方扣留。到晚间，左小诅咒在</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>“</span></span><span><span>豆瓣网</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>”</span></span><span><span>的</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>“</span></span><span><span>左小的小站</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>”</span></span><span><span>发出信息，称被扣留为正常的协助警方调查；</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span></span></span></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span><span>晚上</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span><span>点左右，左小祖咒及妻子、张晓舟等分别向友人发出平安信息“回到宾馆，明天从常州奔牛机场回京。谢谢大家关心”</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span></span></span></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span><span>左小祖咒是艺术家艾未未的好友，</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>4</span></span><span><span>月</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>24</span></span><span><span>日，在摩登天空主办的周庄民谣诗歌音乐节上，左小祖咒在大屏幕上打出声援艾未未的字样。外界疑此番扣留与此有关，左小祖咒本人尚未向外界透露细节。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span></span></span></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span><span>来源：</span></span></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>1、</span><span><span>  </span></span></span><span><span>卫报：艾未未摇滚明星在机场被截留（</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2011.4.27</span></span><span><